OL,5, Russia's best-known conductor Valery   
OL,6, Gergiev has been named head of Moscow's
OL,7, Bolshoi Theatre, alongside his current 
OL,8, role at Russia's other top theatre, the
OL,9, Mariinsky in St Petersburg.            
OL,11,FThe two powerhouses of Russian culture 
OL,12,Fcombine ballet, opera and orchestras.  
OL,14,FGergiev was appointed by Prime Minister
OL,15,FMikhail Mishustin, replacing Vladimir  
OL,16,FUrin, who stepped down at his own      
OL,17,Frequest, the government said.          
OL,19,FFor years he has been an active        
OL,20,Fsupporter of President Vladimir Putin. 
